\c 7
\s AmaIsrayeli abekwa uphawu
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalezizinto-ke ngabona ingilosi ezine\x + 20.8. 9.14.\x* zimi emagumbini womane omhlaba\x + 20.8. 9.14.\x* zibambe imimoya emine yomhlaba\x + Dan. 7.2. Mat. 24.31. Mark. 13.27.\x*, ukuze kungavunguzi moya emhlabeni, kumbe olwandle, loba kwesisodwa isihlahla\x + 6.6; 9.4. 7.1.\x*.
\v 2 Ngasengibona enye ingilosi isenyuka isuka lapho eliphuma khona ilanga\x + Luka 1.78. Hez. 40.6. Isam. 16.12.\x*, ilophawu\x + 9.4. Efe. 1.13.\x* lukaNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + Hlab. 42.2.\x*; yasimemeza ngelizwi elikhulu kungilosi ezine, okwakunikwe kuzo ukona umhlaba lolwandle,
\v 3 isithi: Lingoni umhlaba, kumbe ulwandle, kumbe izihlahla\x + 6.6; 9.4. 7.1.\x*, size siphawule izinceku zikaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 9.4. Efe. 1.13.\x* emabunzini azo\x + Hez. 9.4. Hez. 3.9.\x*.
