\v 4 Ngasengisizwa\x + 9.16.\x* inani elababephawulwa: Zinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amane lane\x + 14.1.\x* abaphawulwayo ezizweni zonke zabantwana bakoIsrayeli;
\v 5 esizweni sakoJuda kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoRubeni kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoGadi kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili;
\v 6 esizweni sakoAsheri kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoNafithali kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoManase\x + Gen. 48.14.\x* kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili;
\v 7 esizweni sakoSimeyoni kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoLevi kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoIsakari kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili;
\v 8 esizweni sakoZebuloni kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoJosefa\x + Gen. 48.14.\x* kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; esizweni sakoBhenjamini kwaphawulwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili.
\s UJohane ubona embonweni abahlengiweyo ezulwini
\p
\v 9 Emva kwalezizinto ngabona, khangela-ke, ixuku elikhulu\x + Roma 11.25.\x*, okungelamuntu ongalibala, elivela kuzo zonke izizwe lemihlobo labantu lezindimi, limi phambi kwesihlalo sobukhosi laphambi kweWundlu\x + 5.9.\x*, lembethe izembatho ezimhlophe\x + 3.4. 7.13,14.\x*, le\add ngatsha\add* zezihlahla zamalala ezandleni zabo\x + Levi 23.40.\x*;
\v 10 njalo limemeza ngelizwi elikhulu, lisithi: Usindiso kuNkulunkulu wethu\x + 12.10; 19.1. Hlab. 3.8.\x* ohlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi, lakulo iWundlu\x + 5.13.\x*.
\v 11 Lengilosi zonke zazimi zihanqe isihlalo sobukhosi\x + 4.4,6.\x* labadala lezidalwa ezine eziphilayo, zasezisiwa ngobuso bazo phambi kwesihlalo sobukhosi, zasezikhonza uNkulunkulu,
\v 12 zisithi: Ameni\x + 5.14.\x*. Ukudunyiswa\x + 5.12.\x* lobukhosi\x + 5.12.\x* lenhlakanipho\x + 5.12.\x* lokubonga\x + 4.9.\x* lodumo\x + 5.12.\x* lamandla\x + 5.12.\x* lengalo\x + 5.12.\x* \add kakube\add* kuNkulunkulu wethu kuze kube nini lanini. Ameni.
\p
\v 13 Omunye wabadala wasephendula\x + Mat. 11.25.\x*, esithi kimi: Laba abembethe izembatho ezimhlophe\x + 3.4. 7.13,14.\x*, ngobani, futhi bavela ngaphi?
\v 14 Ngasengisithi kuye: Nkosi, nguwe owaziyo\x + Gen. 43.20. Mat. 13.27; 21.30; 27.63. Joha. 4.11,15,19,49; 5.7; 12.21; 20.15.\x*. Wasesithi kimi: Laba yibo abaphuma ekuhluphekeni okukhulu\x + Mat. 24.21.\x*, basebehlamba izembatho zabo\x + Isa. 1.18. Zek. 3.3,5.\x* benza izembatho zabo zaba mhlophe\x + 3.4. 7.13,14.\x* egazini leWundlu\x + Heb. 9.14. 1 Joha. 1.7. Isam. 1.5.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho baphambi kwesihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu, bamkhonza emini lebusuku ethempelini lakhe\x + 4.8.\x*; lohleziyo esihlalweni sobukhosi uzabasibekela\x + 21.3. Eks. 25.8. Hlab. 68.18 Hez. 43.7. Joha. 1.14. Levi 26.11. Isa. 4.5,6. Isam. 12.12; 13.6.\x*.
\v 16 Kabasayikulamba, njalo kabasayikoma\x + Isa. 49.10.\x*, lelanga kaliyikuwela phezu kwabo, kumbe lokutshisa\x + Isa. 49.10.\x*\x + Hlab. 121.6. Isam. 16.8,9.\x*;
\v 17 ngoba iWundlu elingaphakathi kwesihlalo sobukhosi lizabondla\x + Hlab. 23.1. Joha. 10.11,14.\x*, libakhokhelele emithonjeni ephilayo yamanzi\x + Hlab. 23.2. Isa. 49.10. Hlab. 36.8. Isam. 14.4.\x*; loNkulunkulu uzakwesula zonke inyembezi emehlweni abo\x + Isa. 25.8. Isam. 21.4. Mat. 5.4.\x*.